---
title: Honey Chicken & Pearl Couscous Bowl with Herby Mayo & Mint
description: Who doesn’t love the signature combo of honey and succulent chicken. With tender pearls of Israeli couscous to soak up all the flavour and a herby hit of dill-parsley mayonnaise, it'll make for a meal that you won’t be able to resist!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
